Definition: plant bearing very hot medium-sized oblong red peppers
Example: grown principally in the Gulf Coast states for production of hot sauce
Synonyms: hot_pepper, tabasco_plant, Capsicum_frutescens, pepper, genus_Capsicum, m, plant, bearing, very, hot, medium-sized, oblong, red, peppers, grown, principally, in, the, Gulf, Coast, states, for, production, of, sauce
Category: noun.plant
